_text = "I regret turning around. Maybe I shouldn't have left so soon. The trip back was too quick. I’m here again. At work.\n\nDon’t get me wrong, I like my job and I like the life I have here, but there’s this craving to explore that haunts my every thought. I crave adventure.\n\nIt consumes my every thought, and returning here after a vacation is almost devastating. I get back into my rhythm, but I feel like the adventure in me is extinguished.\n\nThe flame never fully burns out though. It’s always flickering, waiting to be ignited.\n\nMy memory of this place ends here"

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MemoryTunnelRoom3, MemoryTunnelRoom3, false)
